1.1  This standard covers the requirements for the following types of
spoons made of stainless steel by forging or pressing or a combination
of two processes:
a) Serving spoon, large;
b) Serving spoon;
c) Dessert spoon;
d) Tea spoon, large;
e) Tea spoon, small;
f) Coffee spoon;
g) Soup spoon;
h) Mustard spoon; and
j) Salt spoon.

